{"tid":314137,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"冚黑幫地下竹館荃灣警拉17人","createTime":"2017-07-09T02:27:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-09T02:46:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"13962fc86027c0a0ecdfdab1dacc9ab1219bb7ba","tid":314137,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T02:27:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20083953&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170709\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20083953%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170709&d=9K4m331hoOOF5Vr9VFkABXadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=39edf071\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20083953%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170709&h=6d16dd43\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20083953&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170709</a><br />\n<br />\n冚黑幫地下竹館<br />\n荃灣警拉17人<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】荃灣警區特別職務隊聯同特遣隊人員，根據線報及經深入調查後，昨凌晨約1時展開代號「犁庭掃穴」反罪惡行動，突擊搜查沙咀道290號一單位，搗破一個非法麻雀賭檔。警方拘捕53歲姓梁男主持，涉嫌經營賭博場所，其餘8名男子及8名女子，年齡30歲至63歲，包括兩名持雙程證內地男女，則涉嫌在賭博場所內賭博被捕。<br />\n<br />\n行動中警方撿獲約3,400元水錢、約2,700元賭款、10副麻雀及5張電動麻雀枱。警方相信賭檔由黑幫操控，面積500呎，已運作約兩個月，凌晨零時至清晨運作，專招呼街坊熟客。所有被捕人士正被扣查。"},{"pid":"7cf07435b2b4854585badbaec54feb0bf752d9bc","tid":314137,"uid":62955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T02:35:42.000Z","msg":"3400 水錢，2700賭款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d50bf263a9f7380df3f660a15b0b1cff54a0a16","tid":314137,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T02:40:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>3400 水錢，2700賭款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n黑警cap哂"},{"pid":"1127d952f14b821c48cc9337a083c91af523dc38","tid":314137,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T02:46:32.000Z","msg":"住果頭，出面有個牌寫住會所就無人理"}]}